ISERASE   INIT      "iserase "
TMP0ADAT  INIT      " 27 U1-2,3-14,15-26"
NEZTMP0A  IFILE     SQL, FIXED=27, KEY="U1-2,3-14,15-26"
NAMEA     INIT      "neztmA"
FILENAMA  DIM       8
KILLTMPA  DIM       80
MAKETMPA  DIM       80
.                            * temp file definition
.Name     Type      Length Physical Start Description
.----     ----      ------ -------- ----- -----------
